）（Fabian Picardo）隨即否定加西亞的説法，指先前的地方公投已反對共同管治，強調「不存在任何有關直布羅陀主權會談的空間，連會談的會談對話也不可能」，呼籲直布羅陀居民無須理會。</span><br />\n<br />\n可以公投係咪繼續比英國統治 真心幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:19:00.000Z","msg":"直布羅陀有無 藍絲廢老？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:24:15.000Z","msg":"一定勁少<br />\n公投結果已說明一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2ab09969c162351d9d31cda795aea414412fe7","tid":2509427,"uid":275912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"065794b2fc4858b57362c7990e59908e8e76df6c","tid":2509427,"uid":174246,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:23:37.000Z","msg":"其實都有分別 就係人地9成居民打咗疫苗 香港d反疫苗連登仔就唔撚打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:26:05.000Z","msg":"咁人地打疫苗既死亡率係幾多?"},{"pid":"4ddd842a29aaba7cc571274c19e20569cf7322f3","tid":2509427,"uid":219244,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:31:36.000Z","msg":"西班牙同中共係兩個唔同Level嘅對手喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲國同國之間嘅deal都要睇國力<br />\n<br />\n就好似福克蘭群島好少人，但阿根廷廢得滯，英國佢個數打得過就即刻出兵<br />\n<br />\n但換着對手係中共？香港又冇地理屏障，就算香港有幾百萬人都果斷放棄啦<br />\n<br />\n而且直布羅陀近英國好多，戰略價值亦都大好多<br />\n<br />\n除咗當地居民意願之外，地理位置、聲索國國力全部都係好重要嘅因素"},{"pid":"384b73f9b0cf17df7014c0b6f393e8754a96f6dc","tid":2509427,"uid":256594,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.steamxo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/QdpopU155330_1801212.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.steamxo.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2FQdpopU155330_1801212.jpg&h=4cc9900b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"347bc67ae48d498cc2bbe4c75cf7acf75b531c7b","