ike":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:33:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UYxcJlIcYps\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUYxcJlIcYps&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwVDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=ac483d6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UYxcJlIcYps</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:54:14.000Z","msg":"睇到好吸引<br />\n有機會去行吓先..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:00:31.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"c7a7719cee8606fde139f86b7a270e0f287f89e7","tid":2509427,"uid":252078,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:15:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>從直布羅陀找到英治時期香港的縮影</strong><br />\n<br />\n眾所周知直布羅陀實屬英治區域，不少英倫風格和文化留在於此。看看這些社區設施、學校覺得很眼熟，沒錯這就是說與英治時期的香港非常相近，這裡的門窗、郵箱、電話亭和雙層巴士等回想起小時候的情境，這裡一一呈現出來！戀英戀殖的你，大家會明白。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSQDpGRpxjYToAvg6UrhaqCDaGBr5mbuNqt4VbYQKhrCw?filename=G6qGq1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6qGq1a.jpg&h=aa4a80fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQy9onywca4L3MquHjPpY47WGDyWoscrKy6g5uRFYyTpM?filename=sg9cxGb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsg9cxGb.jpg&h=3d250e88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRzCdXF8RJH8kXniMeRNBh5tADxPGsiXBe3zhajL9wnDg?filename=bVtgZmm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVtgZmm.jpg&h=8735ebd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在每一處紀念碑及政府設施都有前伊利沙伯皇后的徽章，而在香港消失了的龍獅徽在這裡的郵箱等設施顯然可見，亦勾起我童年的回憶。"},{"pid":"6e69809c0a5784419edf668fc9292f4df6bb5e24","tid":2509427,"uid":252078,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:16:21.000Z","msg":"<strong>堅拒不飲「西」水</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUhq3Duk7UcN746d8RVLdJSTeuUPW4eBhmBDH6gzJ29vd?filename=tgXajmH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtgXajmH.jpg&h=ef411a98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n直布羅陀曾因食水問題爭議，在歷史上他們所飲用的水都是來自西班牙。二次大戰後這片殖民地重光，文中沒有因為食水來自西班牙而感恩，卻要求切斷來自西班牙的食水供應，提倡建立於自己的海水淨化系統。<br />\n<br />\n當政府與民眾討論應否自西班牙的水源作自來水，另一方則支持以直布羅陀海峽的水源作自來水之用，而當時人民因此亦曾發起公投，最終以85%的選票取勝以海峽海水作自來水之用。民主的公投暫時不再飲「西」水，而是飲用真真正正來自直布羅陀人的自來水。"},{"pid":"ba4995d636eb1614383250aaa6995abcd75f6d93","tid":2509427,"uid":252078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T16:18:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d6fe3a3d232722140b6afab1937cba635e412292","tid":2509427,"uid":187584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T16:58:30.000Z","msg":"有冇人教佢地咩叫飲水思源<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca395073f2d5ba57d353d74deae4cc8c9a42226f","tid":2509427,"uid":56729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c7a7719cee8606fde139f86b7a270e0f287f89e7","tid":2509427,"uid":252078,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:15:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>從直布羅陀找到英治時期香港的縮影</strong><br />\n<br />\n眾所周知直布羅陀實屬英治區域，不少英倫風格和文化留在於此。看看這些社區設施、學校覺得很眼熟，沒錯這就是說與英治時期的香港非常相近，這裡的門窗、郵箱、電話亭和雙層巴士等回想起小時候的情境，這裡一一呈現出來！戀英戀殖的你，大家會明白。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G6qGq1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6qGq1a.jpg&h=aa4a80fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sg9cxGb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsg9cxGb.jpg&h=3d250e88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVtgZmm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVtgZmm.jpg&h=8735ebd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在每一處紀念碑及政府設施都有前伊利沙伯皇后的徽章，而在香港消失了的龍獅徽在這裡的郵箱等設施顯然可見，亦勾起我童年的回憶。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T17:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a23545a62d3ce22071d218167febdfd81568d0","tid":2509427,"uid":155253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T17:08:55.000Z","msg":"咁當地人係咩人<br /